latestIgtvVideos.title: LA BELLA DEMETRA
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Symbolised by sheaf of Grain, known to the world as “La Regina Del Raccolto”, which in Italian means, “The Queen of Harvest”, Demeter is the Goddess who blesses the humankind with the gifts of fertility, fecundity, and fortune. She is the bearer of an introverted, kind and selfless soul, who rewards people with blessings for even the smallest acts of good they do. She is the one who gave to humanity the knowledge of spirituality to help them live their lives more fully and joyously, as she shared with the world her down-to-earth generosity and wisdom. But mistake her not to be a meek women, for, her wrath against those who attack her and the ones she loves can be as cold as a snowstorm and destructive as a wild forest fire… which is why she symbolises womanhood in its truest essence— possessing profound nurturing love in general that takes mere minutes to transform itself into horrifying fury when attacked by outer forces. 
“La Bella Demtera” is a celebration and an ode to her for blessing the earth with the gift of fertility and fortune and for defining feminity in a complete sense.

latestPosts.caption:
✨ Soft Elegance Meets Radiant Glam ✨

For this stunning beauty, we created a flawless soft glam look that highlights natural features while adding a touch of luxe.

💜 Eyes: A dreamy blend of shimmer purple and pink tones, softly diffused for a romantic vibe. Defined brows frame the eyes perfectly, adding structure without being overpowering.
💋 Lips: A juicy berry gloss adds the perfect pop of color, balancing the softness of the eyes with a fresh, modern finish.
💫 Skin: Dewy, luminous base with just the right glow. Light contouring and a touch of blush keep it youthful and radiant.
🌸 Hair: Soft curls and elegant waves, complementing the overall graceful look.

This look is perfect for cocktail nights, pre-wedding events, or any occasion where you want to turn heads with subtle sophistication.
